PHASE 1 &mdash; PRESERVE (this week)
[ ] Export purchase-order history from Stocky (CSV)
[ ] Export stocktake / adjustment records (CSV)
[ ] Manually record ALL supplier data &mdash; names, contacts, lead times, MOQs (Stocky cannot export suppliers)
[ ] Save exports somewhere outside Shopify (Drive/Dropbox)

PHASE 2 &mdash; CHOOSE (1&ndash;2 days)
[ ] Only need stock tracking/transfers/basic POs? &rarr; Shopify Admin native, done
[ ] Need an order-driven stock ledger you own? &rarr; free Make.com + Google Sheets route ($0)
[ ] Need forecasting/reorder automation? &rarr; shortlist a paid tool ($29&ndash;$120/mo bracket)
[ ] Multi-channel (Amazon/eBay/Etsy)? &rarr; sync-first tool
[ ] Manufacture from raw materials? &rarr; BOM-capable tool (Katana/Craftybase class)

PHASE 3 &mdash; DEPLOY IN PARALLEL (same day)
